{"word":"ἴσος","slug":"ἴσος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἴσος, η, ον</el></b> [related to <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἶδος\">εἶδος</a></el>] <b>equal</b> of amount, size, or status <b><a href='B:470 20:12'>Mt 20:12</a>; <a href='B:500 5:18'>J 5:18</a>; <a href='B:730 21:16'>Rv 21:16</a>;</b> <el>τὰ ἴσα</el> equal amount <b><a href='B:490 6:34'>Lk 6:34</a>;</b> <el>ἡ ἴσα <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δωρεά\">δωρεά</a></el> the same gift <b><a href='B:510 11:17'>Ac 11:17</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pl.\">pl.</a> functions as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> in the phrase <el>ἴσα εἶναι</el> be equal to <b><a href='B:570 2:6'>Phil 2:6</a>.</b> Of testimony <b><a href='B:480 14:56'>Mk 14:56</a>, <a href='B:480 14:59'>59</a>,</b> in both <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a>: their testimony did not jibe, was inconsistent. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἰσκαριώθ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἰσότης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}